er; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3);">与圣人的精神接通、相会</span></span></strong></p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 541.594px; height: 3em; line-height: 3.2em; display: inline-block; background-image: url(&quot;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/76621600_1555491176.cn/mmbiz_png/trcftmucdribhe620ksrjsu2x1m3lgooatc9vxejpj1hddhqpk0fln6dktkciagg9ro98kthd6l6iauaric3t6sb1w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-size: contain; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 17px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">文以载道</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(123, 12, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(123, 12, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">中国文字，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;">即是：凝聚中国文化的文字，亦可说是怀抱圣王道德的文字。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">丁亮老师在《中国文字之道》，曾讲到“神”这个字，左边一个“礻”，右边一个“申”，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">甲骨文里的“申”字，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3);">就是闪电啊，哗的一下，直接下来，</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">圣人的神也一直延伸，延伸到我们的今天，通过这个有形的文字，跨越时空，传递那个无形的精神，</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3);">看到的这个字，就如圣王在我们面前，我们就能跟他们的精神接通、相会。</span></p><p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">汉字不只是对于事物之形体的描绘，更是通达之人以心应万物而体会到的事物之神。如虽然意思变了，但依然没有背离字本身的意象。汉字并不是凭空造出的符号，它与天地人紧紧联结。因此，它所蕴含的内容极其丰富又极其精炼，</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">屯字的甲骨文，破土而出的小芽生动地概括了所有这一切的主题，甚至不需要多余的解释。这就是汉字的魅力、灵性所在。不是被人为赋予含义的符号，而是直接取之于天地，新鲜活泼，无可辩驳，无所隔阂。</span></strong><br/></p><p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 541.594px; height: 3em; line-height: 3.2em; display: inline-block; background-image: url(&quot;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/91134600_1555491176.cn/mmbiz_png/trcftmucdribhe620ksrjsu2x1m3lgooatc9vxejpj1hddhqpk0fln6dktkciagg9ro98kthd6l6iauaric3t6sb1w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-size: contain; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 17px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">过化存神</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; width: 677px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; width: 677px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">过就是经，经过。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">存者，在也，还在。</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3);">过化，存神，这些格与上下，通达天地的圣人们，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">虽然已经过世了，但是他们的</span>精神还在！透过每个饱满、有力的文字，延伸至今！</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在上次的台湾行中，王镇华老师带大家去参访一座清朝遗留下来龙潭圣迹亭。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3);">老师说：古人敬天惜字，写好的字不能随意丢弃，各地都会盖起敬字亭，供书迹墨纸的焚烧。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">烧纸时，每一个字都像一只蝴蝶，飞到天上，告诉仓颉：人们没有乱用你造的字。在圣迹亭的面前，感受到</span>先辈对文字深切的敬意与珍惜。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(3, 3, 3); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; paddin