 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;">有诗曰：</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">明月何皎皎，照我罗床帏。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">忧愁不能寐，揽衣起徘徊。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">客行虽云乐，不如早旋归。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">出户独彷徨，愁思当告谁！</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">引领还入房，泪下沾裳衣。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: right;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: right; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">来源：《昭明文选》</span><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">明这个字的重要，是给我们人生带来一丝光明意念，而此是自明的神明，或明神</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">在迷茫时，不忘记自己过去对自己的期许，初心自明！</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word 