normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">每天一集，</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">每集6—15分钟，</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">伴您365天，</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">与丁亮老师一起，</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%;"><span style="font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 透过文字，</span></span></span><span style="font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &