c: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;">明字古文字取月之光華以表意，囧或為滿月，月則為弦月。</span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;">说起”明“，我们会想到明月、明白、清明、明天、明理，明智、明明德……</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;">有诗曰：</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">明月何皎皎，照我罗床帏。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">忧愁不能寐，揽衣起徘徊。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">客行虽云乐，不如早旋归。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">出户独彷徨，愁思当告谁！</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(122, 68, 66); font-size: 15px;">引领还入房，泪下沾裳衣。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: right;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: right; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">来源：《昭明文选》</span><span style="max-width: 100%; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">明这个字的重要，是给我们人生带来一丝光明意念，而此是自明的神明，或明神</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">在迷茫时，不忘记自己过去对自己的期许，初心自明！</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-weight: bolder; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><br/></span></span></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; widows: 1; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><font color="#c00000"><b>您将获得</b></font></p><p style="widows: 1; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><font color="#c00000"><b><br/></b></font></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">每天一集，</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">每集6—15分钟，</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">伴您365天，</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 34px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">与丁亮老师一起，</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%;"><span style="font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 40.3125px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(3, 3, 3); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 透过文字，</span></span></span><span style="font-weight: bolder; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &